<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><strong>3) Core Web Vitals &amp; technique</strong></p>\\n<ul style=\\\"margin-top: 0cm;\\\" type=\\\"disc\\\">\\n<li class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3;\\\">Vise un LCP &lt; 2,5 s, CLS &lt; 0,1.</li>\\n<li class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3;\\\">Optimise images (WebP), lazy-loading, mise en cache, compression.</li>\\n<li class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3;\\\">Corrige les erreurs d&rsquo;exploration et canonicals.</li>\\n</ul>\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><strong>4) Maillage interne &amp; E-E-A-T</strong></p>\\n<ul style=\\\"margin-top: 0cm;\\\" type=\\\"disc\\\">\\n<li class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo4;\\\">Lien depuis les pages piliers vers les contenus de soutien.</li>\\n<li class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo4;\\\">Ajoute des preuves d&rsquo;expertise (auteur identifi&eacute;, sources, mise &agrave; jour dat&eacute;e).</li>\\n</ul>\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><strong>5) Mesure &amp; am&eacute;lioration continue</strong></p>\\n<ul style=\\\"margin-top: 0cm;\\\" type=\\\"disc\\\">\\n<li class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5;\\\">Suis positions, trafic organique et conversions.</li>\\n<li class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5;\\\">Observe la SERP pour d&eacute;tecter les nouveaux formats et adapter la page.</li>\\n</ul>\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><strong>&Agrave; retenir :</strong> publie moins mais mieux, et it&egrave;re &agrave; partir des donn&eacute;es.</p>\", \"seo_data\": \"{\\\"meta_title\\\":\\\"TUTO ET Guide complet pour optimiser le SEO en 2025\\\",\\\"meta_description\\\":\\\"\\\\u2022\\\\tExtrait (meta r\\\\u00e9sum\\\\u00e9)\\\\r\\\\nUn guide clair et actionnable pour am\\\\u00e9liorer la visibilit\\\\u00e9 Google en 2025 : mots-cl\\\\u00e9s, contenu, Core Web Vitals, maillage interne et su\\\",\\\"canonical_url\\\":null,\\\"robots\\\":{\\\"index\\\":true,\\\"follow\\\":true}}\", \"updated_at\": \"2025-10-24 06:54:39\"}',NULL,NULL,NULL,'127.0.0.1','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64; rv:144.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/144.0',NULL,'2025-10-24 04:54:39','2025-10-24 04:54:39'),(335,'a030b08a-7362-47c5-9fa6-433a10c49e88',NULL,3,35,'update','{\"comment_count\": 132}',NULL,NULL,NULL,'127.0.0.1','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64; rv:144.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/144.0',NULL,'2025-10-24 10:43:27','2025-10-24 10:43:27'),(336,'a030b094-f06a-4eef-a9e9-554cc5ad7981',NULL,3,35,'update','{\"comment_count\": 134}',NULL,NULL,NULL,'127.0.0.1','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64; rv:144.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/144.0',NULL,'2025-10-24 10:43:34','2025-10-24 10:43:34'),(337,'a030b0af-2dff-4fb8-905a-9da59b9b9532',NULL,3,35,'update','{\"comment_count\": 134}',NULL,NULL,NULL,'127.0.0.1','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64; rv:144.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/144.0',NULL,'2025-10-24 10:43:51','2025-10-24 10:43:51'),(338,'a030b0af-3060-47c7-9434-e76147521682',NULL,3,35,'update','{\"comment_count\": 135}',NULL,NULL,NULL,'127.0.0.1','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64; rv:144.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/144.0',NULL,'2025-10-24 10:43:51','2025-10-24 10:43:51'),(339,'a030b70b-5127-43d2-a70a-3a9fac4208ed',NULL,3,35,'update','{\"comment_count\": 137}',NULL,NULL,NULL,'127.0.0.1','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64; rv:144.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/144.0',NULL,'2025-10-24 11:01:38','2025-10-24 11:01:38'),(340,'a0366527-b677-4942-95e6-0f0d0b91061b',NULL,14,35,'update','{\"deleted_at\": null, \"updated_at\": \"2025-10-27 08:47:36\"}',NULL,NULL,NULL,'127.0.0.1','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64; rv:144.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/144.0',NULL,'2025-10-27 07:47:38','2025-10-27 07:47:38'),(341,'a0366528-6951-4084-bfa5-55de063f8b66',NULL,14,35,'update','{\"status\": \"published\", \"updated_at\": \"2025-10-27 08:47:38\"}',NULL,NULL,NULL,'127.0.0.1','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64; rv:144.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/144